    <field id="description" text-type="text/html"><![CDATA[Lets assume we have a complex change request and we need to document our changes and impact analysis for our customer. 
<ul>
  <li>Create a new space with name <span style="font-style: italic;">Change Requests<br/>
    </span><br/>
    
    <table id="polarion_wiki macro name=table;params=width=600px" class="polarion-Document-table" style="width: 600px;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;border: 1px solid #CCCCCC;empty-cells: show;border-collapse: collapse;">
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <th style="font-weight: bold;font-size: 9pt;background-color: #F0F0F0;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;vertical-align: top;height: 12px;border: 1px solid #CCCCCC;padding: 5px;">Hint: Select <span style="font-style: italic;">Documents &amp; Wiki</span> in your navigation bar </th>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <br/>
    <img src="attachment:createspace.jpg"/><br/>
    <br/>
  </li>
  <li>Add a favorite shortcut for your new space <span style="font-style: italic;">Change Requests<br/>
    </span><br/>
    <img src="attachment:favorite.jpg"/><br/>
  </li>
  <li>Create a new document in space <span style="font-style: italic;">Change Requests</span> and name it <span style="font-style: italic;">Impact Analysis Simple Search Extension</span></li>
  <li>Configure your document that all of the following work items are allowed in your document (for all work items title and description should be shown on document):<br/>
  </li>
  <ul>
    <li>Requirement</li>
    <li>Task</li>
    <li>Change Request</li>
    <li>Test Case<br/>
      <br/>
      <img src="attachment:configure-2.jpg" style="width: 709px;height: 479px;"/><br/>
      <br/>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <li>Move your change request to your document using work item action menu<br/>
    <br/>
    <img src="attachment:move.jpg"/><br/>
    <br/>
  </li>
  <li>Add Heading <span style="font-style: italic;">Needed Tasks</span> and move the related task to this chapter.<br/>
  </li>
  <li>Add Heading <span style="font-style: italic;">Requirements</span> and add references to all affected requirements<br/>
    <br/>
    <img src="attachment:in.jpg" style="width: 724px;height: 399px;"/><br/>
    
    <table id="polarion_wiki macro name=table;params=width=600px" class="polarion-Document-table" style="width: 600px;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;border: 1px solid #CCCCCC;empty-cells: show;border-collapse: collapse;">
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <th style="font-weight: bold;font-size: 9pt;background-color: #F0F0F0;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;vertical-align: top;height: 12px;border: 1px solid #CCCCCC;padding: 5px;">Hint: You can use Copy&amp;Paste to add a reference to a work item also. </th>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <br/>
  </li>
  <li>Add Heading <span style="font-style: italic;">Test Cases</span> and add references to all affected test cases<br/>
  </li>
  <li>Add modification for requirement by using work item overwrite option<br/>
    <br/>
    
    <table id="polarion_wiki macro name=table;params=width=600px" class="polarion-Document-table" style="width: 600px;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;border: 1px solid #CCCCCC;empty-cells: show;border-collapse: collapse;">
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <th style="font-weight: bold;font-size: 9pt;background-color: #F0F0F0;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;vertical-align: top;height: 12px;border: 1px solid #CCCCCC;padding: 5px;">Hint: These modified/new requirements can be moved to correct specification document later on and replaced by their reference in our impact analysis document </th>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </li>
</ul>]]></field>
